snippet.title: Blood will be Spilled -  Nintendo Switch Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Blood will be Spilled - Story of revenge, blood, bullets, and insects coming to Nintendo Switch on February 20, 2020.

Nintendo NOA: https://bit.ly/2tR2hXm
NintendoEU: https://bit.ly/39p0dVv
Steam: https://bit.ly/2Sfu8K4
Artbook: https://bit.ly/2UDxW9L
Price: $14.99 / €14.49

Hi guys,
a few months ago, we decided to help our friends from Doublequote Studio bring their first game Blood will be Spilled to Nintendo Switch. 

Follow them on:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/doublequoteStd
Facebook: https://facebook.com/bloodwillbespilled
Web: https://www.bloodwillbespilled.com
